ğŸ“Œ New agent-config1.yml (Contains Routing Processor)
yaml
Copy
Edit
processors:
  ## ğŸ”„ Routing Processor - Send Logs to Different Destinations
  routing:
    from_attribute: service.name
    table:
      "frontend-service":
        exporters: [otlphttp]
      "backend-service":
        exporters: [logging]

service:
  pipelines:
    logs:
      processors: [routing]
